Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.27,0:00:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}要想建造横贯大陆的铁路\NTo build the transcontinental railroad,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.92,0:00:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}"大佬"托马斯·杜兰特曾经说过\NThomas "Doc" Durant once said
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.73,0:00:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}一个人必须面对心中的恶魔  然后摧毁它们\N"A man must face his demons and destroy them
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.39,0:00:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}否则就会受其影响  无所作为\Nor become undone by them."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.56,0:00:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}1868年的地狱之轮可不是这些人该待的地方\NThe hell on wheels of 1868 is no place for bashful men,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.69,0:00:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}害羞  轻信和无把握之人\Nthe deluded, or unassured.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.20,0:00:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}以及邋遢鬼  穿着圣服的醉鬼和疯子\NNo place for sloppy men, drunk and disorderly in their heavenly vestments
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.69,0:00:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他们的半只脚已踏进坟墓\Non their way to an early grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.69,0:00:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}过去三年里  铁路通过火车\NThe railroad has contained the west these last three years,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.25,0:00:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}和铺在地上的铁轨控制了西部\Nwith its iron horse and rails pinned to the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.65,0:00:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}日复一日  即使它没有带来礼仪\NAnd each passing day brings with it civilization,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.74,0:00:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}也带来了文明\Nif not civility.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.66,0:00:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}穿着制服的文明人们  如今用钢笔做着\NAnd men in suits, who do now with their pens
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.33,0:00:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}之前粗鲁的人们用枪做的事\Nwhat earlier, rougher men did with their guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.45,0:01:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}卡伦·博汉南  联太公司前任总工程师\NCullen Bohannon, late of the Union Pacific,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.69,0:01:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}更像个枪手  而不是文明人\Nis more gunman than suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.85,0:01:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他回到了夏安镇  如今它被称为\NHis return to Cheyenne; these days referred to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.62,0:01:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}平原上的魔幻城镇\Nas the "Magic city of the plains,"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.24,0:01:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他在草原上消失了几个月  人们以为他死了\Nafter months lost to the prairie and presumed dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.76,0:01:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}现在却带着摩门妻儿归来\Nwith a Mormon wife and child in tow,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.77,0:01:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他也许正是我们所需的润滑剂\Nmight be just the grease we need
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.09,0:01:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}来推动全国痴迷的铁路建设\Nto turn the wheels of our national obsession,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.50,0:01:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}让漫长的冬季随雪消融\Nburied these long winter months in snow
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.29,0:01:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}由泥土中的车辙决定未来\Nand now, up to its wheel-wells in mud.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.22,0:01:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}或者说  这是他自我牺牲的开始\NOr might it be the match strike of self-immolation?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.21,0:02:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}因为博汉南先生一贯的正直\NFor Mr. Bohannon has always worn his integrity
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.46,0:02:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}亦是他的负担\Nlike a millstone around his neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.32,0:02:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}好啊\NHowdy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.13,0:02:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}要帮忙吗\NHelp you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.04,0:02:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你可以让开\NYou can step aside.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.36,0:02:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}博汉南回来了\NBohannon's back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.75,0:02:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}-你来这里干什么  -不关你的事\N- What's your business here? - None of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.74,0:02:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你听到了吗  警官\NHa. You hear that, deputy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.48,0:02:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这不关我们的事\NIt's none of our business.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.87,0:02:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}摩门教徒在这里只会遇上麻烦  朋友\NThere's nothin' here for Mormons but trouble, friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.04,0:02:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我不是来找麻烦的\NI ain't lookin' for trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.60,0:02:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}在我的镇上  麻烦刚好就会找这种人\NJust the kind of people trouble finds in my town.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.63,0:02:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}西北部五六十英里有摩门教徒的聚居地\NThere's a Mormon settlement 50, 60 miles to the northwest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.23,0:02:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你们在那边会受到欢迎的\NYou'll be welcome there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.20,0:02:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}放开我的马\NLet go of my horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.62,0:03:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}放开我的马\NLet go of my horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.34,0:03:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}别碰我\NDon't touch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.74,0:03:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你最好听她的\NI'd listen to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.09,0:03:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我建议你转过身来\NI suggest you turn around and--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.02,0:03:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他还是挡了我的路\NStill blockin' my horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.15,0:03:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}谢谢\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.62,0:03:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}驾\NLet's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.01,0:04:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}卡伦·博汉南回来了  亲爱的读者们\NCullen Bohannon has come home, dear reader.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.43,0:04:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}在这个文明世界以西的小镇里\NAnd in our little world just west of civilization,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.30,0:04:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们发现自己又一次任他摆布\Nwe find ourselves once again at his mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.52,0:04:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你是说  挖一条\NAre you telling me it's impossible
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.81,0:04:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}穿山隧道是不可能的吗  没人能做到\Nto tunnel through that mountain? No man can do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.19,0:04:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们已经炸了一周多了\NWe've been blastin' for more than a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.12,0:04:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}该死的山一直坍塌\NDamn thing keeps caving in on itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.65,0:04:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}天啊  德莱尼\NGod sakes, Delaney.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.76,0:04:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}内华达山脉没挡住亨廷顿\NThe Sierra Nevadas couldn't stop Huntington.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.42,0:05:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这个小山丘也不能阻挡我\NThis blip of a molehill is not going to stop me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.31,0:05:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}内华达山脉由花岗岩组成  杜兰特先生\NThe Sierras are made of granite, Mr. Durant.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.10,0:05:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这里的岩层更不稳定\NWe're dealing with more unstable terrain here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.36,0:05:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}泥岩和页岩\NMudrock and shale.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.32,0:05:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}借口可不会帮我建好隧道\NExcuses will not get my tunnel built.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.88,0:05:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你尽一切努力吧\NNow, do whatever you have to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.93,0:05:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}让工人加班清除碎石\NPut on an extra shift to clear the rubble
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.43,0:05:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}印更多代金券付给他们\Nand print up more scrip to pay the men.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.13,0:05:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他们不会白白干活的  被自由人也不会\NThey won't work for nothing, not even the freedmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.05,0:05:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}杜兰特先生...\NMr. Durant--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.35,0:05:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}就这样  谢谢  德莱尼\NThat will be all. Thank you, Delaney.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.32,0:05:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这里是铁路办公室\NThis is the railroad office,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.99,0:05:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不是售票厅\Nnot the ticket office.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.38,0:05:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}售票厅在后面\NBehind the building.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.34,0:05:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}铁轨对面的车站那边\NAcross the tracks at the depot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.49,0:05:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我是卡伦·博汉南  来见杜兰特\NCullen Bohannon. Here to see Durant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.07,0:06:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我是马丁·德莱尼\NMartin Delaney.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.39,0:06:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}石溪大桥建造者\NBuilder of stone and brook bridges.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.21,0:06:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}联合太平洋铁路首席工程师\NChief engineer at the Union Pacific.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.00,0:06:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}卡伦·博汉南的鬼魂来了\NIt's the ghost of Cullen Bohannon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.69,0:06:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}现在竟然是摩门教徒\NAnd...Mormon, no less.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.25,0:06:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}如果有证据表明你无法被杀死\NIf ever there was proof that you cannot be killed,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.09,0:06:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那这就是了\Nthis is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.01,0:06:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}上次我看到你时  你正被一群蒙面歹徒\NThe last time I saw you, you were being dragged away
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.40,0:06:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}拖走  此后便再无踪迹\Nby a gang of masked outlaws, never to be seen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.70,0:06:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}带我走的是她爸爸\NIt was her dad who took me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.95,0:06:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}摩门民兵因为...\NMormon militia on account of the--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.08,0:06:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这是我妻子娜奥米  我儿子威廉\NThis is my wife Naomi and, uh, my son William.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.63,0:06:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们在史密斯保卫站过的冬\NWe wintered up at Fort Smith.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.67,0:06:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}虽然出了些事  不过我现在回来了\NTook some doin', but I'm back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.03,0:06:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那你为了逃出来  杀害了多少\NAnd how many Mormons did you have to put in the ground
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.95,0:06:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}摩门教徒\Nto effect your escape?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.54,0:06:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不是那样的\NWasn't like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.06,0:06:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你总是那样  博汉南\NIt's always like that with you, Bohannon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.55,0:07:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你在我的镇上引发了一场枪战\NYou start a gunfight in my town,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.13,0:07:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}差点把我们都害死  为什么\Nnearly have us all killed, and for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.12,0:07:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}就因为一个被你搞大肚子的姑娘\NA girl you got pregnant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.80,0:07:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我是回来工作的  我能恢复原职吗\NCome back for my old job. Is it mine or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.07,0:07:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不  不能\NNo. Not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.78,0:07:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你的铁路停滞不前  杜兰特\NYour railroad's stuck, Durant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.18,0:07:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}只有我才能让它再继续前进\NI'm the only one who can get it movin' again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.10,0:07:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}即使我可以解雇德莱尼先生\NEven if I could fire Mr. Delaney,
