Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.30,0:07:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}为人可靠\Ndependability.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.24,0:07:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你要想继续建造铁路\NWhat you need to get this road movin' again
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.11,0:07:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}就需要一个能让你翻过谢尔曼峰的人\Nis a man who can get you over Sherman Summit, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.82,0:07:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}而他做不到\NHe ain't him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.86,0:07:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我不是要翻过去  博汉南\NI am not going over, Bohannon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.91,0:07:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我要穿过去\NI am going through.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.53,0:07:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}而且不用你的帮助\NAnd without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.75,0:07:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}欢迎来到夏安镇  女士\NWelcome to Cheyenne, madam.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.68,0:08:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}事情不像我计划的那么顺利\NThis ain't how I planned on things goin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.41,0:08:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}夏安镇也不像我想象中那么美好\NThis ain't how I pictured Cheyenne.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.55,0:08:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我会想办法的\NI'll figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.36,0:08:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们一起想办法\NWe'll figure it out together.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.96,0:08:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}上车吧\NCome on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.72,0:08:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}博汉南先生\NMr. Bohannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.95,0:08:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你的到来真是雪中送炭啊\NYou are a sight for sore eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.82,0:08:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}刚好在我以为自己的好运用完的时候\NJust when I thought me luck had run out,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.44,0:08:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你就来了\Nhere you be.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.14,0:08:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你这是怎么了\NWhat happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.38,0:08:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我跟一个摩门教的姑娘结婚了\NGot a Mormon girl in the family way,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.34,0:08:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}现在需要一份工作\Nand I need a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.38,0:08:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}还有什么问题吗\NAny more questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.71,0:08:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}格兰特派了个投机之人\NGrant sent a carpetbagger out
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.78,0:08:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}来这里实行法律维护秩序\Nto install law and order.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.94,0:08:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他绞死了一个我赌场里面的人\NHe hung a man from the rafters of my casino.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.58,0:09:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我现在正需要一个你这样的人\NI could use a man like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.26,0:09:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不了  谢谢\NNo, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.11,0:09:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你刚才不是说需要一份工作吗\NYou just said you needed a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.42,0:09:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不是那种工作\NNot that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.35,0:09:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}很高兴见到你  米奇\NIt was good to see you, Mick.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.06,0:09:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}对了  我现在是镇长了\NBy the way, I'm the mayor now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.88,0:09:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}恭喜了\NCongratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.70,0:09:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他是你的好友吗\NIs he a close friend of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.44,0:09:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他杀了自己的兄弟  是我帮他埋的\NKilled his brother, and I helped to bury him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.88,0:09:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这样我们应该算有点交情吧\NSuppose that makes us somethin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.59,0:09:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这杆枪可花了我28美元\NI paid $28 for this rifle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.31,0:09:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你可以去找他报仇\NYou can take it out of his hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.80,0:09:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}什么时候\NWhen?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.67,0:09:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我让你去的时候\NWhen I tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.98,0:09:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这个保加利亚人不简单\NA rare Bulgarian, that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.94,0:09:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}可以不知不觉就把你眼皮子地下的东西偷走\NSteal the milk out your tea as soon as he look at ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.98,0:10:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是联合太平洋铁路公司的测量师\NA surveyor for the Union Pacific.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.97,0:10:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}杜兰特先生的雇员\NAn employee of Mr. Durant
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.47,0:10:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}刚好也是我赌场的\Nwho happens to be a partner
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.87,0:10:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}一个合作伙伴\Nin my casino.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.96,0:10:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他臭了\NHe stinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.78,0:10:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}把他弄走\NGet him out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.25,0:10:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你们自己弄吧\NI'll leave that to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.70,0:10:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}把他弄走  麦克吉尼斯\NGet him out of here, McGinnes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.43,0:10:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他现在是你们的烂摊子了\NHe's your trash now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.92,0:10:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}下次你们再在我的地盘\NAnd next time ye decide to turn my business
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.32,0:10:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}绞死人...\Ninto a gallows...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.06,0:10:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}走之前给我清理干净\Nyou clean up before you leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.58,0:10:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}两位  告辞\NGentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.90,0:10:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}吁\NHo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.96,0:10:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你来吃午饭吗\NYou coming to lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.00,0:10:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你的东西\NThis yourn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.69,0:11:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}早知道你会回来  我就不动\NI knowed you's comin' back, I'd have guarded
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.37,0:11:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}藏在东西里的那些钱了\Nwhat little money was hid backside and front.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.53,0:11:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那可让我们改善了一个月伙食\NThat money fed us good for a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.47,0:11:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}还好好喝了一顿\NBought us one hell of a hangover, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.31,0:11:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你帮我找个工作  钱就不计较了\NIf you give me a job, we'll forget about the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.61,0:11:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你可不是黑人  博汉南先生\NYou ain't been in the sun long enough for that, Mr. Bohannon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.44,0:11:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我有家要养\NI got a family to feed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.91,0:11:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}跟我干  报酬和黑人一样\NFreedman work, freedman wages.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.93,0:11:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}很公平\NFair enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.51,0:11:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}从没想过我有天能成头儿的头儿\NNever thought I'd see the day I'd be the boss of the boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.97,0:11:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}别高兴太早  帕萨姆\NDon't get used to it, Psalms.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.57,0:11:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}露丝\NRuth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.75,0:11:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我正想去找你呢\NI was just on my way to see you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.74,0:11:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}今天我们都吓到了  是不是\NWe all got the shock of our lives today, didn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.20,0:11:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}博汉南先生回到夏安镇了\NW-With Mr. Bohannon's return to Cheyenne.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.19,0:12:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是的\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.14,0:12:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这几个月我都在祈祷他回来\NI've been praying these many months for such a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.35,0:12:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你还好吗  露丝\NHow are you, Ruth?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.58,0:12:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}依然在祈祷\NStill praying.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.97,0:12:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你住在这  应该没人会找麻烦\NReckon nobody'll start a war if you stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.79,0:12:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}挺好的\NIt'll do just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.05,0:12:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}给\NHere.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.01,0:12:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}吃吧\NEat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.57,0:13:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}好  我抱\NYeah, there we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.79,0:13:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}听着\NNow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.01,0:13:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}遇到麻烦  可以去找牧师\NYou have trouble on the way, you can see church lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.83,0:13:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}她叫露丝  会帮你的\NHer name's Ruth, she'll help.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.34,0:13:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我不用人帮\NI won't need any help.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.81,0:13:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我没事的\NI'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.93,0:13:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们没事的\NWe'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.94,0:13:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你觉得呢\NWhat you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.41,0:13:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你会没事吗\NYou gonna be fine?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.35,0:13:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我猜你回来露丝小姐挺高兴\NI expect Miss Ruth happy you're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.38,0:13:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你失踪她很难过\NTook it hard the day you gone missin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.77,0:13:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}也一直在照顾那个男孩\NGot her hands full with that boy, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.80,0:13:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我猜她发现你娶了妻\NI expect she won't be none too happy
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.18,0:13:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不会太高兴\Nshe find out you got yourself a new woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.88,0:13:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}还生了孩子\NNew baby, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.46,0:14:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}又一个女人来找你麻烦了\NUh-oh. Here come your other woman problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.26,0:14:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}埃兰为找你被害了\NElam went after you and got his self killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.27,0:14:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}埃兰向来我行我素\NElam went his own way, as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.61,0:14:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}伊娃  冷静\NEva, calm down now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.52,0:14:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你消失了  他去找你\NYou disappeared and he went after you,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.63,0:14:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}向来都是\Nas always!
