Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.32,0:31:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}确实不是  先生\NNo, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.29,0:31:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}过来\NCome here!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.87,0:31:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}如果人们相信他们中有人能凌驾于法律之上\NIf people believe any one of them is above the law,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.07,0:31:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那法律就形同虚设\Nthere will be no law.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.06,0:32:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你是说杜兰特吗\NDurant?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.58,0:32:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我想问问韦伯法官关于重建的意见\NI'd like to ask Judge Webber his opinion on a remedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.06,0:32:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这个点  你应该能在赌场\NThis hour, you're likely to find him
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.87,0:32:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}或者妓院里找到他\Nat the Faro Tables or the whorehouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.25,0:32:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是  先生\NYes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.97,0:32:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}走开  走开\NGet off! Get off!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.38,0:32:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}今天怎么样  丈夫\NHow was your day, husband?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.50,0:32:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}还不错\NIt was fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.40,0:32:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}-你呢  -还行吧\N- Yours? - Just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.48,0:32:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}博汉南先生\NMr. Bohannon.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.29,0:32:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你在里面吗\NYou in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.39,0:32:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}博汉南先生\NMr. Bohannon.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.19,0:33:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}坎贝尔州长\NGovernor Campbell.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.56,0:33:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}很高兴再次见到你  博汉南太太\NWhy, it's nice to see you again, Mrs. Bohannon.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.81,0:33:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}如果你有话要对我妻子说\NYou got somethin' to say to my wife, son,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.06,0:33:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}跟我说就行了\Nyou talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.09,0:33:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我只是想说我给她买了顿饭\NI bought her a meal is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.96,0:33:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你喜欢吗\NHow you enjoyin' it?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.75,0:33:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我可以自己买\NI can buy my own meals.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.70,0:33:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你昨天跟我的人发生了冲突\NYou handled yourself mightily with my men yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.98,0:33:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我跟他们说过了  我不想找麻烦\NLike I told 'em, I ain't lookin' for trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.86,0:33:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}各位晚安\NY'all have a good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.06,0:33:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}格兰特将军非常看重你  博汉南先生\NGeneral Grant holds you in high regard, Mr. Bohannon.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.23,0:33:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你想怎么样\NWhat do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.86,0:33:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}像你这种身份的人却混迹于一帮...\NA man of your stature livin' amongst the, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.65,0:33:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}黑鬼吗\NNegros?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.75,0:33:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}自由人\NFreedmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.07,0:33:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你没必要住在这种肮脏的地方  博汉南先生\NNow, you don't have to live in squalor, Mr. Bohannon.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.03,0:33:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你为我工作  我会给你体面的工资\NYou work for me. I'll pay you a decent wage.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.98,0:33:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我已经有工作了\NI already got a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.95,0:33:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我会付你铺铁轨的三倍工资\NI'll pay you three times what you make layin' rail.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.26,0:33:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}还会为你的家人建一所房子\NAnd I'll help you build a house for your family.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.40,0:34:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}在那之前  请允许我为你在旅馆订个房间\NUntil then, allow me to engage a room for you at the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.61,0:34:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}热水澡  暖和的床\NHot bath, warm bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.63,0:34:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你今晚就可以过去  博汉南太太\NYou could be there tonight, Mrs. Bohannon.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.54,0:34:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}为投机者工作吗\NWork for a carpetbagger?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.80,0:34:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}绝对不可能\NNot a chance in a hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.34,0:34:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}先生  我相信日后人们\NThe Freedmen's Bureau, sir, is but one legacy
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.57,0:34:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}会因自由民局而记住我\Nof reconstruction I believe I shall be remembered for.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.57,0:34:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}格兰特建立的机构  旨在帮助黑人  促进黑人和白人合作
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.80,0:34:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}并爱戴我\NAnd fondly.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.00,0:34:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}如果你改变主意的话  来找我\NShould you change your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.28,0:34:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我数了一下  我们到这之后\NBy my count, that's two good jobs
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.56,0:34:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你已经拒绝了两份好工作\Nthat you've turned down since we got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.67,0:35:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们接下来该怎么办\NWhat're we meant to do then?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.86,0:35:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}娜奥米\NNaomi...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.33,0:35:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我所做的一切\NEverything I done...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.90,0:35:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我杀过的人  带来的毁灭\Nall the death and destruction I put my hand to
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.49,0:35:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}和承受过的痛苦\Nand was put to me--
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.28,0:35:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}如果不建完这条铁路  这些都将沦为徒劳\Nall that is for naught if I don't finish this road.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.32,0:35:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}博汉南先生\NMr. Bohannon.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.96,0:35:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}没想到你居然还在这里\NSurprised you're still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.86,0:35:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我也是\NLikewise.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.78,0:35:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这里确实有种魔力\NSomethin' about the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.46,0:35:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这里的菜很好  毫无疑问\NThe cuisine, no doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.21,0:35:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我以为你早就逃回纽约了\NThought you would have hightailed it back to New York by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.25,0:35:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}故事把我留在了这里\NStory keeps me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.00,0:36:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}小心别让故事害死你\NCareful it don't kill ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.11,0:36:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你还没被害死呢\NHasn't killed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.20,0:36:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}暂时没有\NYet.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.02,0:36:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我听说你结婚了\NI hear you got married.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.67,0:36:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是的\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.43,0:36:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}摩门淑女\NNice mormon girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.86,0:36:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我对你的故事很感兴趣  博汉南先生\NI'm interested in your story, Mr. Bohannon.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.32,0:36:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我的读者也是\NMy readers will be as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.51,0:36:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这不是故事  埃里森小姐\NAin't a story, Miss Ellison.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.62,0:36:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}只是生活而已\NJust a life.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.36,0:36:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}自己的生活自己过  没必要让别人读\NIt's mine to live, nobody's to read about.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.00,0:36:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我\NOh, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.11,0:36:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}抱歉打扰你们用餐\NSorry to interrupt your supper.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.13,0:36:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我想过来打个招呼\NThought I should come by and say howdy.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.50,0:36:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们以为你死了\NWe thought you were dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.05,0:36:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你们为什么这么想\NWhy'd you think that?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.57,0:36:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不然你会回来的\NYou would have come back otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.82,0:36:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}去外面等着  孩子\NWhy don't you go wait outside, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.57,0:37:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}去吧\NGo on.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.90,0:37:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}以斯拉很想你  博汉南先生\NEzra has missed you, Mr. Bohannon.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.87,0:37:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他为你哀伤\NHe grieved for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.68,0:37:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我也是\NAs did I.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.64,0:37:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你把他带得很好  他长高了\NYou done right by him. He's growin' up tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.42,0:37:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是的\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.40,0:37:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们俩现在相依为命\NWe're our own little family now.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.33,0:37:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}只有我们俩\NThe two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.34,0:37:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}露丝\NRuth--
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.99,0:37:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我很抱歉\NI'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.45,0:37:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}现在你回来了\NNow you're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.78,0:37:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}带着新妻儿\NWith a new wife and child.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.40,0:38:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我相信随着铁路向前铺\NI'm sure as the railroad starts moving,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.84,0:38:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你也会跟着一起走\NYou'll be moving with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.30,0:38:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我要照料教堂\NI have my church to look after.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.70,0:38:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}还有那孩子\NAnd the boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.55,0:38:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们会留在这里\NWe'll be staying here.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.08,0:38:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我来是想求你帮忙\NI come to ask a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.95,0:38:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我觉得我帮不上你什么\NI don't think I can help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.77,0:38:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}娜奥米和我儿子  威廉\NNaomi and my boy, William...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.19,0:38:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我去挖路基时  他们没人照顾\NWhen I'm out in the cut, they're here all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.82,0:38:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我知道你看不惯\NI know how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.34,0:38:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}摩门教徒\NAbout Mormons.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.74,0:38:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我希望如果需要的话\NI was hopin' you could find it in your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.33,0:38:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你能发发善心\Nto lend a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.44,0:38:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}伸出援手\NIf need be.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.06,0:38:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我建立这座教堂的目的就是为贫苦之人\NI have built the walls of my church to be a stronghold
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.42,0:38:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}提供一个避风港  博汉南先生\Nfor the needy, Mr. Bohannon.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.80,0:39:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}如果某天你的妻儿来到了教堂门前\NShould your wife and child ever find themselves at my door,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.59,0:39:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}正如对镇里的任何人一样\Nthey, like everyone else in this town,
